{"tid":1496384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［置頂]聽晚識巴絲教學，同場仲有快速單身配對！！","createTime":"2019-08-22T13:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T17:32:34.000Z","uid":295218,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6634ea637f6cdc35bb4456158d38fbffd4a4cf6e","tid":1496384,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，你班仆街可唔可以膠少陣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日開親連登都見到講聽日拖手仔嘅post <br />\n你地到底係為咗岀嚟抗爭定係識男女朋友？<br />\n仲有個madam <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班仆街仲記唔記得點解要岀嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔對得住呢兩個月犧牲嘅人？<br />\n有無諗過佢地或佢地嘅屋企人見到嘅啲文會點？<br />\n<br />\n依加係叫你地岀嚟抗爭，唔係叫你地去玩<br />\n可唔可以尊重下成個運動同參與嘅手足？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地係為咗可以拖手仔又好，為咗識另一半都好<br />\n我制止唔到你地嘅諗法，但可唔可以唔好講岀嚟？<br />\n尋日係元朗又係咁，默站緊又叫口號<br />\n到底你地知唔知咩叫尊重？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e03887f27a25099bac2ba152fe1b50afb52621e","tid":1496384,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:33:34.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"3f2f8f3ed5bd7146d64306ac4cc6cef3c14c2798","tid":1496384,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:33:46.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"076f721539000bdff8daac180b00b532e311a040","tid":1496384,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:34:01.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"626ba2602ac83b7153dffb893a9ba40ed76febab","tid":1496384,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:34:11.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"ecc9f265398edbd2eebf94a88a3617ee0c0c8313","tid":1496384,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:34:21.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"0e938d93e5b8a7fb2d13852bf4608f72979b878c","tid":1496384,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime